content.rendered:
University of Florida Spring 2023 Career Fair

Tuesday, February 7, 2023

9:00 AM – 1:00 PM

O’Connell Center

Info Session: An info session will be held on Monday, February 6 from 1:00 PM – 3:00 PM in Rinker Hall.

 

For more information, visit UF’s Career Events site.
